      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p>@Icon[type:graviton]Graviton Revelation</p>\n<p>As a standard action, you can cause a cloud of debris, microscopic particles, and small items to orbit you, trapped in your personal gravitational field. This grants you @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.Kjba2E3Ad5oMJ7hV.JournalEntryPage.nyB6pt2dd6iVQGmS]{Concealment} against ranged attacks. This ability functions for 1 round or until you leave graviton mode.</p>\n<p>When you are attuned or fully attuned, the cloud of debris and microscopic particles thickens, increasing the miss chance from your concealment to 50% on ranged attacks (though you are not considered to have total concealment).</p>"
